des: Hourly air quality information provided by AirNow. Please see AirNow.gov for information on the agencies that are credited with the source data for air quality reports. AirNow observational data are not fully verified and validated and should be considered preliminary. As such, they should not be used to formulate or support regulation, guidance, or any other government or public decision.
